            <div class="faq-questions__body-items active" data-category="general">
                <!-- questions and answers -->
                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general1">
                        "How do I find my bracelet, anklet, or choker size?"

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general1" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            We offer many tips on finding your right size, you can see sizing help 
                            <a target="_BLANK" title="Automic Gold Sizing Guide" href="https://www.automicgold.com/pages/sizing">here</a>. 
                            For bracelets/anklets: Measure your wrist or ankle with a soft tape measure leaving about a fingers-width of room so it isn’t too tight or loose. 
                            For necklaces/chokers: Measure in inches the length of a chain you already have or use a soft tape measure around your neck to where you want your chain to sit.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general2">
                        “I don’t know my size, should I order a ring sizer from you?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general2" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            It is not necessary to order a ring sizer from us, especially if your order is time sensitive. All ring sizers are in the standard size. If you don’t know your size go to a local jewelry shop or purchase a ring sizer locally. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general-modify" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="general3">
                        “Can I modify an item in your collection?”
                
                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                
                    <div id="general-modify" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            Yes! We can customize almost any of our products. You can <a title="Email Automic Gold Care" href="mailto:care@automicgold.com">Contact Us</a> for any customization requests. However, any
                            modified jewelry will become final sale and will no longer be eligible for return or exchange.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general3">
                        “Can my order be canceled?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general3" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            Yes, we will cancel an order that has not been shipped. If the order was shipped please refuse the package upon delivery. 
                            When it comes back to us we will issue a refund.  Custom and engraved jewelry cannot be canceled.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general4">
                        “Can you change the shipping address?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general4" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            We cannot change shipping address once an order has been placed. The fulfillment will be cancelled and you can place a new order with the updated shipping address. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general5">
                        “I put the wrong billing address, can you change it?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general5" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            Unfortunately, we have no way of changing the billing address. If you received an order confirmation email then the 
                            order went through without any issues and we are working on getting your order to you. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general6">
                        “I did not receive an order confirmation and my card was charged.”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general6" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            Please double-check the email address you used and spam folders. The confirmation may have gone to an email address 
                            you don’t frequently use. If you are still unable to find the order confirmation, it is likely the order did not go 
                            through. The charge on your card will drop off in 2-3 business days, if it does not, please contact your bank for 
                            further details.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general7">
                        “I chose the wrong metal color/size/initial, can you change it?” 

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general7" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            If the order has not been shipped, we can make changes. We only ask that you contact us in a timely manner. Engraved and final sale items can not be changed.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general8">
                        “What fonts do you offer for engraving?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general8" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            We automatically do a block font. We do not offer a list of fonts but we can do any free font that can easily be retrieved. 
                            It is encouraged to provide the name and style for reference. We can also engrave in other languages. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general9" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general9">
                        “I have a metal allergy, can I wear your jewelry?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general9" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            It depends on the metals you’re allergic to. If you have a nickel allergy, it is best to order yellow gold or rose gold 
                            items as white gold contains a small amount of nickel. You can view the breakdown of metal percentages <a title="Automic Blog: Why Does Gold Have Different Colors?" target="_BLANK" href="https://www.automicgold.com/blogs/automic-blog/why-does-gold-have-different-colors">here</a>.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general10" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general10">
                        “I emailed and haven’t heard back.”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general10" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            We operate Monday-Tuesday and Thursday-Friday from 9am - 5pm, with the exclusion of holidays. Your email is important to us and it is our intention 
                            to connect in a timely manner. We do experience high volume orders and emails, your patience and cooperation is greatly appreciated. 
                        
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general11" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general11">
                        “Do you offer in person pick-ups?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general11" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            Please contact us for further information. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general12" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general12">
                        "I would like to collaborate with Automic Gold, who do I reach out to?"

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general12" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            For all collabs please reach out to <a title="Email Automic Gold" href="mailto:hello@automicgold.com">hello@automicgold.com</a>. We will reach back out if we see that it's a good fit.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general13" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general13">
                        “I thought this is solid gold, why is it changing color/tarnishing?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general13" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            This is totally normal and we can assure you it’s only “dirt”. This tends to happen mostly with earring posts. 
                            The mixture and accumulation of our natural bodily/external oils, bacteria and chemicals from product build up 
                            can cause the discoloration. Simply rub the posts with jewelry polishing cloth to clean it.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general14" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general14">
                        “Do you offer internships?” 

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general14" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            We are thrilled that you’re interested but unfortunately, we do not offer internships. We hire full time and long term employees. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general15" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general15">
                        “Do you offer wholesale?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general15" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            At the moment we do not have the capability. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general16" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general16">
                        “What items are final sale?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general16" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            All custom, engraved or any modified items are considered final sale. All pierced body jewelry is also final sale.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general17" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general17">
                        “What is Route?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="general17" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            Route is a package protection company that offers protection against lost, stolen or damaged packages. It also gives up-to-date tracking information for your order once it ships. For more information, check out <a target="_BLANK" aria-label="Learn more about Route" href="https://route.com/">Route</a>.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general18" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="general18">
                        “Can I cancel/make changes to my customized or engraved order?”
                
                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                
                    <div id="general18" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            Once you place the customized/engraved order - it enters the production stage and it is final sale. We can not do any modifications or cancelation.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general19" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="general19">
                        “What forms of payment do you take?”
                
                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                
                    <div id="general19" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            We accept all major credit & debit cards, PayPal, Shop Pay, Affirm & AfterPay.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

               <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#general20" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="general1">
                        "Do you have a warranty?"

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>                  
                    <div id="general20" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            Yep! All of our pieces come with a <a href="https://www.automicgold.com/pages/lifetime-warranty" target="_blank">limited lifetime warranty</a> that covers manufacturer defects for up to three years after receipt. We don’t cover normal wear & tear, loss, or loss of parts, and all warranties are voided if your item has been modified by other jewelers. If you notice any loose stones or suspicious defects, <a href="mailto:care@automicgold.com">let us know</a> right away. We recommend getting insurance for all jewelry over $10,000. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            
