                            than expected. If you need your order sooner please contact us to upgrade your shipping method - additional shipping fees may 
                            apply. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#shipping3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="shipping3">
                        “I placed a custom order, when will it ship?” 

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="shipping3" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            Please contact our custom department <a target="_BLANK" href="https://www.automicgold.com/pages/custom-orders" title="Automic Gold Custom Orders">here</a> for all custom related questions. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#shipping4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="shipping4">
                        “Do I need to sign for the delivery?”

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="shipping4" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
                            Signatures on orders are optional! You can choose if you'd like to include a signature at checkout. However, we highly
                            recommend the signature option as it safer for your package. If you choose to have your package delivered without a
                            signature, Automic Gold is not responsible if the package is lost or stolen.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-questions__body-item">
                    <button class="btn faq-questions__btn" type="button" data-target="#shipping5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="shipping5">
                        “Can I check the status of my order?” 

                        <svg width="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6-1.41-1.41z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="shipping5" class="faq-questions__answer-block">
                        <div class="faq-questions__answer-card">
